Package org.training.foodorderapplication.repository

package org.training.foodorderapplication.repository
This package contains the repository interfaces for the Food Order Application. The interfaces provide methods to access and manage data in the underlying database.

The package contains the following interfaces:

FoodItemQuantityRepository - provides methods to access and manage FoodItemQuantity entities in the database.

FoodItemRepository - provides methods to access and manage FoodItem entities in the database.

FoodOrderQuantityRepository - provides methods to access and manage FoodOrderQuantity entities in the database.

FoodOrderRepository - provides methods to access and manage FoodOrder entities in the database.

UserRepository - provides methods to access and manage User entities in the database.

VendorRepository - provides methods to access and manage Vendor entities in the database.

By using these repository interfaces, the Food Order Application is able to interact with the underlying database and manage data in a structured and efficient manner.
